		&lt;li&gt;9&lt;sup&gt;th &lt;/sup&gt;January -&amp;nbsp;Pravasi Bharatiya Divas NRI Day&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;11&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; January -&amp;nbsp;Death anniversary of Lal Bahadur Shastri&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;12&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; January -&amp;nbsp;National Youth Day (Birth Day of Swami Vivekanand)&lt;/li&gt;
