&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jeddah, Saudi Arabia.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India rejected the Organisation of Islamic Cooperation&amp;rsquo;s (OIC) statement on the recent terrorist attack in Pahalgam, Jammu and Kashmir.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Ministry of External Affairs described the statement as factually incorrect, absurd, and misleading.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India accused Pakistan of influencing the OIC to issue the statement and reaffirmed that Jammu &amp;amp; Kashmir is its internal matter.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Organisation of Islamic Cooperation (OIC) is headquartered in &lt;u&gt;Jeddah, Saudi Arabia&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;India rejected the OIC&amp;#39;s statement on the Pahalgam attack as misleading and externally motivated.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The OIC was criticized by India for allegedly acting under Pakistan&amp;rsquo;s influence regarding Kashmir.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;India reiterated that Jammu and Kashmir is an integral part of India and foreign interference is unacceptable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);  &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Organisation of Islamic Cooperation (OIC)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Formed in - 1969&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Headquarters - Jeddah, Saudi Arabia&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Total Member States - 57&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Secretary-General - Hissein Brahim Taha&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s Stand on OIC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
