&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legal Information Management and Briefing System.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Union Minister of State for Law and Justice, Arjun Ram Meghwal, inaugurated the &lt;strong&gt;Legal Information Management and Briefing System (LIMBS)&lt;/strong&gt; in New Delhi.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;LIMBS is designed to enhance &lt;strong&gt;transparency, accountability, and efficiency&lt;/strong&gt; in government litigation management.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The LIMBS &lt;strong&gt;Live Cases Dashboard&lt;/strong&gt; provides details of all cases scheduled in the next seven days in various courts, including the Supreme Court and High Courts.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The system allows officers and ministers to monitor case updates directly from their offices and receive real-time information on upcoming cases.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Currently, the LIMBS portal holds details of around &lt;strong&gt;7 lakhs live cases&lt;/strong&gt; from 53 Ministries and Departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LIMBS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;: A digital platform developed to manage and track legal cases in a centralized system, enhancing decision-making and coordination among government ministries.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Live Cases Dashboard&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;: A feature of LIMBS that provides real-time data visualization of court cases, allowing stakeholders to proactively manage legal proceedings.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ministries and Departments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;: Various government entities whose cases are tracked on LIMBS, making it easier to manage their legal affairs and ensure timely actions.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data-driven insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;: The use of real-time data to optimize case management, ensure faster resolution, and improve governance outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

